<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause id="_49767c38-74dc-408c-a277-9137d6df4003" outputclass="ncc-clause" variation="TAS"><sptc>E2P1</sptc><title id="_fa48ebf6-b417-421d-a69e-27a1711b6611">Design, construction, installation and maintenance</title><archive-num>2019: GP1.1</archive-num><subclause id="_c5e04c0f-fed9-4879-ba46-97bbb3fce3f8" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_743d6777-35ef-426b-a45c-9d0bfebd2636">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>A mechanical service, plant and equipment for heating, cooling and/or ventilation must avoid the following:</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_eebdaeca-3521-4c7c-b42f-dcb5a5da7769">Damage to property.</li><li id="_ad5e80b0-3746-4f61-862e-a5562684bef4"><xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1362_2.0.0.xml#_ba5bd5ee-ef5f-41be-b153-43835028cd86" id="_35847dc6-74b9-4bfe-aeee-6ffb5117292a" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">Loss</xref> of <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1186_0.6.0.xml#_905252bf-2ff1-43f8-ae81-2949aa116fee" id="_57a12ec3-22ef-4c3e-b75a-d1793b25fb5c" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">amenity</xref> to occupants.</li></ol></subclause><subclause id="_d5a1c9f9-a626-4594-9a97-bdb6eaa58af6" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_d47f5443-039e-4939-aadc-b742e195d2d6">SubClause</title><num>2</num><p>A mechanical service, plant and equipment for heating, cooling and/or ventilation must ensure the following:</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_6ece89d2-bc9c-432e-b13b-7041730ba1de">Efficient use of energy and water.</li><li id="_e32f7cc6-6d7d-4702-b6dc-a55f225426d9">Access for maintenance.</li></ol></subclause></clause>